# Nicholas Trimble — Portfolio

![Portfolio Logo](images/logo.png)

## Overview

This is my personal software engineering portfolio showcasing full-stack applications, backend systems, and data-driven tools built with C#, Python, and JavaScript.

I focus on building **backend systems, real-time applications, and data processing workflows** that solve real operational problems.

---

## 🚀 Featured Work

### 🏥 HospitalFlow — Real-Time Hospital Resource System
ASP.NET Core MVC • SignalR • EF Core • PostgreSQL  
Real-time system for synchronizing hospital resources and preventing conflicting updates across users.

### 🚨 IncidentLink — Emergency Dispatch System
ASP.NET Core MVC • SignalR • PostgreSQL  
Dispatch and resource allocation system with concurrency-safe assignment logic and real-time updates.

### 🛠 AssetOperations — Work Order Tracking System
ASP.NET Core MVC • EF Core • SQL Server  
Asset lifecycle tracking system using service-layer architecture, authentication, and audit logging.

### 📊 Python Data Systems
Django • Flask • ETL Pipelines • APIs  
Built data pipelines and dashboards for transforming operational data into analytics and visual insights.

